Assembly is a type of code that only has the code that you need to do what you are telling it to do. It is good got wrting divers, system desgins, embedding systems, and hybrid codes. Assembly is diffrent from java because it is just used for speed, it only has what is needed. A high-level language is portable, you program faster, have less lines and easier to mantian. Low level are more bare and are fast and has control over system hardware. Java is a high level language becasue it is easy to code and mantian. Assembly is a low level it is harder to write but it was direct communication to the system.
